<br>
IMO dodger is prety poor for mercenaries compared to Mastery of Parrying, which enables us to get off our 'offensive' stun better. ALso the chance to aprry is 1/2'd when vs a 2H weapon used. You can point out that it works the other way around- a s/s Warrior wil only block half as much, but that's simply because he's fending off two attaks per round. Correct me if I'm wrong.<br>
<br>
Some mercs love having shield, but I never bothered with it. Also there's the problem of having to manually change weapos through the inventory if you want to switch your shield for a Left Hand weapon.<br>
